.TH hint 1 "November 2025" "hint 1.0.0"
.SH NAME
hint \- fast, Starship-ready command palette for the terminal
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B hint
.RI [ i | --all | --doctor | --debug ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B hint
prints short, practical command hints grouped by category. It integrates with the
Starship prompt via a small module (\fBsysline\fR) that shows username, load, RAM,
disk and battery status.

Interactive mode
(\fBhint i\fR) uses \fBfzf\fR if available; press Enter to paste/execute
the selected command.

.SH FILES
.TP
~/.config/hint/custom.sh
Optional per-user hints. Each line must be TAB-separated:
\fICATEGORY\fR\t\fILABEL\fR\t\fICOMMAND\fR\t\fIWHY\fR

.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B HINT_ROOT
Override the detected project root.
.TP
.B HINT_HINTDIR
Override the path to the \fIhint/\fR categories directory.
.TP
.B HINT_CUSTOM_FILE
Change the per-user custom hints file (default: ~/.config/hint/custom.sh).
.TP
.B HINT_PLUGIN_DIRS
Colon-separated list of extra roots that include hint/ folders.

.SH SEE ALSO
.BR fzf (1), 
